Resources,

applications, maps, and visualizations created by City staff and the community build using the City of Austin's open data.

City Clerk's Office

Campaign Finance Data Search

Users can search campaign finance data submitted to the City Clerk between 2016 - present.

Austin Watershed Department

ATX Floods

Using open data, ATXfloods is an application which informs you about low water crossings across Central Texas during flooding events.

Transportation Department

Transportation Dashboard

View the real-time open data about signal operations accessible to
everyone.

visualizations

Lobbying in Austin

An experiment with data visualization for the city's lobbyists registration database

Applications

Cute Pets Austin

Twitter bot that posts random adoptable pets from the Austin Animal Center dataset.

Maps

Austin Green Map

Map of Austin's parks: users can search parks with BBQ Pits, restrooms, tennis courts using Austin Parks data.
